item.description: Alfred - TryHackme’s Room Writeup This my first attempt at creating a writup, I tried putting every single step I took to solve this room. While providing enough (I think) details and descriptions so it is useful for noobs like me mostly. I started drafting this at the same time I managed to solve a question or even right after thinking a way to approach a solution for any of those.
